Rivers United win title, and qualify alongside Plateau United for 2022/2022 CAF Champions League Remo Stars qualify for 2022/2023 CAF Confederation Cup competition Katsina United, Heartland FC, Kano Pillars and MFM FC are all relegated to the lower league. Kano Pillars had six points deducted from them for disciplinary issues. (NAN)(www.nannews.ng)   Edited by Olawale Alabi